Class ErrorDetailsDto

java.lang.Object
com.jsacristan.word_card_back.dtos.ErrorDetailsDto
public class ErrorDetailsDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object for representing error details. This class is used to encapsulate details about errors that occur.
